OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,FBaroness Sue Gray, who was formerly
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer's chief of staff, has
OL,8,Fexpressed fears for the future of
OL,9,FStormont.
OL,11,FThe Labour peer previously worked as a
OL,12,Fsenior civil servant in both Whitehall
OL,13,Fand in Northern Ireland. She once
OL,14,Fmissed out on becoming the head of the
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland Civil Service.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
