PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,FShe was the author of the party-gate
OL,7,Finvestigation report into social
OL,8,Fgatherings at Downing Street under the
OL,9,Flast Conservative government during
OL,10,FCovid lockdowns and went to become a
OL,11,Fkey member of Sir Keir's team when he
OL,12,Ffirst took office as Prime Minister.
OL,14,FBaroness Gray later quit the role in
OL,15,FOctober 2024 after weeks of reports of
OL,16,Finfighting in Number 10 and headlines
OL,17,Fabout her salary. She was elevated to
OL,18,Fthe House Lords four months later.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
