FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,FThe former permanent secretary at
OL,7,FStormont's Department of Finance was
OL,8,Fin Belfast on Thursday to take part in
OL,9,Fan event organised by the SDLP that
OL,10,Fexamined relations between the island
OL,11,Fof Ireland and Britain and prospect of
OL,12,Ffuture constitutional change.
OL,14,FIn her contribution, she made a case
OL,15,Ffor greater collaboration between
OL,16,FWhitehall and the devolved
OL,17,Fadministrations in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,F"I think there is a feeling, and I
OL,7,Ffelt this when I was in the Department
OL,8,Fof Finance, you know, my colleagues,
OL,9,Fthey were my colleagues in the UK
OL,10,Fgovernment, there were people that I
OL,11,Fwould have sat down with before I'd
OL,12,Fcome here, and I would go back and sit
OL,13,Fdown with, and, you know, I wasn't
OL,14,Finvolved in discussions," she said.
OL,16,F"I would get a phone call on the
OL,17,Fmorning of a new policy with some
OL,18,Ffunding.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@YO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,F"How that could have been so different
OL,7,Fif the devolved government had sat
OL,8,Fround that table and had contributed
OL,9,Fto that discussion, and I do think
OL,10,Fthat is something that we need to do
OL,11,Fmore of."
OL,13,FThe peer also expressed concern about
OL,14,Fhow devolved government was currently
OL,15,Ffunctioning at Stormont.
OL,17,F"I do fear for Stormont, and I do
OL,18,Fthink that people here deserve action
OL,19,Fand decisions, and that is a joint
OL,20,Fresponsibility across many people,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@IO]yD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
