PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,FBaroness Gray advocated introducing a
OL,7,F"metro mayor" model across the
OL,8,Fdevolved regions to give city
OL,9,Fauthorities more powers to take
OL,10,Fdecisions. In Northern Ireland, she
OL,11,Fsuggested metro mayors for Belfast and
OL,12,FLondonderry.
OL,14,FShe also voiced support for Andy
OL,15,FBurnham's reported plan to move part
OL,16,Fof the Downing Street operation to
OL,17,FManchester if he becomes prime
OL,18,Fminister.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,417,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,F"I do think actually taking and just
OL,7,Festablishing an office outside Downing
OL,8,FStreet, outside London and the South
OL,9,FEast, sends a really powerful signal,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"It sends a very powerful signal to
OL,13,Fgovernment departments who, you know,
OL,14,Fdo think everything happens in
OL,15,FWhitehall and London."
OL,17,FBaroness Gray said she hoped Mr
OL,18,FBurnham was equipped to see off the
OL,19,Fchallenge posed by Reform UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]tD@AOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
