PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1782505102
OL,3,CBaroness Sue Gray says she 'fears for
OL,4,CStormont'
OL,6,FShe told the event in Belfast: "If
OL,7,FAndy is the successor (to Sir Keir), I
OL,8,Fthink that his experience, not just in
OL,9,Factually, you know, working in
OL,10,FManchester, he's also worked in
OL,11,FWhitehall previously and held
OL,12,FSecretary of State positions, so he
OL,13,Fcan bring a lot of experience to the
OL,14,Ffore."
